### Summary of Failure
The `google_model_armor_template.j1_trajectory_shipper` resource failed because the Model Armor service requires the linked SDP (DLP) template to be in the **same location** as the Model Armor template. The plan attempted to link a regional Model Armor template (`us-central1`) to a global DLP template.
